ainst another breaker named Molly in the WDSF Oceania Breaking Championships, Raygun displayed some of the unique moves that made her a viral sensation on Friday night.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 0.8762769392475758, \"rank\": 0.14119172549047315, \"text\": \"Oceania\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oceania_Football_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 874, \"end\": 880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0952414239127519e-20, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another breaker\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"the unique moves\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday night\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately for the dancer, real name Rachael Gunn, there will be no chance for a reprieve in four years time with breakdancing set to be axed from the Los Angeles Olympics.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999998733529, \"rank\": 1.0147433752377533e-10, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1018, 